Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Shah flees Iran
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bwfz
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 21 Jan 1979
Shah of Iran loses power, flees country with famaily. Exiled Ayatollah expected to return from Paris. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less